"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-paris-olympics-previewing-every-sport\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics are here, and SI has the perfect podcast to guide you through the Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 91, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure you subscribe toSports Illustrated\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Daily Rings, hosted by Mitch Goldich and Dan Gartland.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9998304428439156, \"rank\": 0.00016645583910134231, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\", \"score\": 0.9999996835124921, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gartland\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The podcast will release new episodes every day of the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the Olympics started, the two hosts gave rapid-fire previews of all 39 sports, focused on structure, format, changes from previous Olympics, top names to know, key story lines and favorites.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe wherever you get podcasts (includingAppleorSpotify) and look for clips onSI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s YouTube page.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The previews are split into two episodes.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Episode 1 covers archery, artistic swimming, boxing, badminton, beach volleyball, basketball, breaking, 3x3 basketball, cycling, canoeing, fencing, diving, golf, equestrian, handball, field hockey, modern pentathlon, gymnastics and rhythmic gymnastics.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 776, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9998816855777525, \"rank\": 0.00011832831445363439, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Episode 2 covers judo, sailing, rowing, shooting, rugby, skateboarding, sport climbing, soccer, swimming, surfing, table tennis, taekwondo, tennis, track and field, trampoline, triathlon, water polo, volleyball, wrestling and weightlifting.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.9913492576098455e-13, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profi